d use an polyline to represent a road or the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"path along which something moves.","type":"text"}],"title":"MLNPolyline","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline","fragments":[{"text":"MLNPolyline","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS/BuildingLightExample":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre-native-for-ios\/buildinglightexample","kind":"article","role":"article","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Add a fill extrustion layer and adjust the light dynamically with a slider."}],"title":"Fill Extrustion Layer","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS\/BuildingLightExample","type":"topic"}}}